        "creation_date": 1585809771,
        "body": "<p>Public is a key word in java so you can't use public as a name for an attribute or variable. (See also <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Java_keywords\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Java_keywords<\/a>) <\/p>\n\n<p>You have to rename the attribute inside your POJO class. For example publicAttr or something like that.<\/p>\n",
        "answer_id": 60985622,
